message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "exact-pi: Exact ten-million-digit decimal prefixes of pi in dependency-free TypeScript"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-07-15
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/AlbatrossMicrosystems/exact-pi"
authors:
  - family-names: Ghosh
    given-names: Sagnik
